Artur's build of the st terminal emulator (st-0.8.4)
----------------------------------------------------

Main features of the fork:
The following patches were adapted to work with st-0.8.4 and applied:
    1. st-alpha: Patch that allows transparent terminal window -- https://st.suckless.org/patches/alpha/
    2. st-xresources: This patch adds the ability to configure st via Xresources -- https://st.suckless.org/patches/xresources/
    3. st-font2: This patch allows to add spare font besides default -- https://st.suckless.org/patches/font2/
    4. st-clipboard: Shared clipboard between text-based apps and X apps -- https://st.suckless.org/patches/clipboard/
    5. st-rightclickpaste: Pressing right-click pastes from the primary-selection -- https://st.suckless.org/patches/rightclickpaste/
    6. st-scrollback: Allows scrollback through terminal output -- https://st.suckless.org/patches/scrollback/
    7. st-scrollback-mouse: Allow scrollback using mouse wheel -- https://st.suckless.org/patches/scrollback/
    
Changed some default keybinding.
Added the ability to tweak opacity level via the Xresources file.
